WEBVTT

00:00.919 --> 00:03.556
_

00:06.646 --> 00:10.282
Are you going to spend the entire
holiday behind your newspaper?

00:17.842 --> 00:19.237
Ecco. (Voilà.)

00:19.704 --> 00:20.904
Happy?

00:28.726 --> 00:29.926
Sì.

00:32.106 --> 00:33.495
Time for my run.

00:33.533 --> 00:35.154
Sun is still too strong.

00:35.177 --> 00:36.597
Ah, nonsense.

00:37.674 --> 00:39.618
Takes work to look this good.

00:42.001 --> 00:43.601
I love you, you know?

00:45.739 --> 00:47.036
I know.

00:53.982 --> 00:55.324
Have a good run.

